name: Warmup_Div04_Sub01
queryText:
SELECT DISTINCT
GmailD4S1.CPF,
GmailD4S1.NOME,
GmailD4S1.EMAIL,
GmailD4S1.EMAIL_VALIDO,
CASE

  WHEN CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD4S1.NOME) = 0 THEN GmailD4S1.NOME

  ELSE SUBSTRING( GmailD4S1.NOME , 1, CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD4S1.NOME) )

END AS PNOME
FROM Gmail_DIV04_SUB01 GmailD4S1
UNION
